Friends only.
add first, then comment.

Last chance, if I've added you on my new name and you want to be my friend still, add me back. If I haven't added you and you want me to, let me know. If we aren't mutual friends I might start dropping people soon.

I'm starting on the transition over to my new journal. If you get a random friend request, it's most likely from me. If I didn't add you, I either know you too personally, we don't communicate enough, you never update, or I just missed your name. If you think I missed your name by mistake or you really want to be added leave a comment. :)

Post a picture in my comments of what you think describes me when you think about what/who I am. No matter how surreal or plain.

Give no written explanation.

Just an image.

(Optional: Post this in your journal and see what images you get.)
